# Migrate OldComponent to NewComponent

Welcome to the migration of OldComponent into NewComponent, here we will see how to easily migrate to NewComponent component.

## One of the main changes is...

A description of it...

Example:

```tsx
import { OldComponent } from '@ultraviolet/ui'

const MyComponent = () => (
  <OldComponent>
      My text
  </OldComponent />
)
```

Becomes:

```tsx
import { NewComponent } from '@ultraviolet/ui'

const MyComponent = () => (
  <NewComponent>
      My text
  </NewComponent />
)
```

